Added caption support to the Video block. New schema fields `showCaption` (boolean, default `true`), `title`, and `description` are rendered below the player using the `Caption` component from `@kitconcept/volto-light-theme`. Caption `title` and `description` are prepopulated from the selected Video content item's `Title` and `Description` (both via the in-block picker and the sidebar object browser) when the fields are empty. @ericof
